### Extract Article
POST http://localhost:3000/api/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://example.com"
}

###

### Plan Slides
POST http://localhost:3000/api/plan-slides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "This is a test article about Docker. Docker is a containerization platform. It uses images and containers.",
  "tone": "Educational",
  "slideCount": "auto"
}

###

### Fill Visual Data
POST http://localhost:3000/api/fill-visual-data
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visualType": "step-chain",
  "title": "How Docker works",
  "body": "First you build an image. Then you run a container."
}

###

### Regenerate Block
POST http://localhost:3000/api/regenerate-block
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "block": {
    "type": "CONTENT",
    "title": "Old Title",
    "body": "Old body content.",
    "order": 1
  },
  "instruction": "Make it more exciting"
}
